  [ Emilio Pozuelo Monfort ]
  * debian/patches/CVE-2017-7870-poly-oob-write.diff: fix CVE-2017-7870.
  * debian/patches/olefix35.diff: fix CVE-2017-3157. Initial patch
    by Rene Engelhard. Backported additional change to embedhlp.cxx to
    check if updating links is allowed before doing so.

