openoffice.org (1:2.4.0~ooh680m6-3) experimental; urgency=low

  * ooo-build:
    - update (r11531)
  * debian/control.in:
    - make -calc conflict against openoffice.org-common (<< 1:2.3.0)
      (closes: #464544)

 -- Rene Engelhard <rene@debian.org>  Fri, 08 Feb 2008 00:19:05 +0100

