     - bump libdb4.2-java builddep to libdb4.2-java (>= 4.2.52-21) for sid
     - remove obsolete libxp-java and libjaxp1.2-java builddeps (leave
       libjaxp1.2-java for sarge, though, as we need to use Suns JDK...)
     - fix control.help.in
